releases.body:
- Upgrade to Electron v1.4.8
- Separate dissector utilities as [driptool](https://www.npmjs.com/package/driptool) package

# Release Node
- Update to npm 4.0.2
- Fix broken `Buffer#toString('hex')`

# Release Note
- Upgrade to Electron v1.4.7
- Performance improvements
- Fix broken RPM #9

## Release Note
- Upgrade to Electron v1.4.6
- Fix a crash in Session destructor
- [PacketFilterView] improve response to mouse clicks

releases.name: v0.4.5
releases.body:
# Release Note
- Improve display filter performance
- Support auto-completion for display filter
- Fix a crash caused by referring the same layer twice in a display filter

## Release Note
- Reduce app size and dependent packages
- Fix a crash caused by GC
- [PacketView] Add filter hints

## Release Note
- Enable --harmony-async-await in renderer processes
- Support traversing packets with keyboard in PacketListView https://github.com/dripcap/dripcap/issues/5
- Fix pcap import erroneously starting capture
- Simplify dissector APIs

releases.name: v0.4.2
releases.body:
## Release Note
- Fix BPF not working.
- Fix layer attributes not being accessible through display filter.
- Improve display filter performance.
